original_title: 隣のゴミ部屋キモオッサンに軟禁され絶倫チ〇ポで犯され続けた私 神木蘭
overview: Kamiki Ran moves to live in a new apartment alongside her boyfriend and they soon discover that the next-door neighbor is a deranged old man in his 60s, who lives among piles of thrash.  One day Ran goes to complain to the neighbor about the noise. But this old guy, in view that her boyfriend was away, decides to invite her inside his place, against her will.
title: [FSDSS-569] I Was Confined To The Garbage Room Next Door And Continued To Be Fucked By An Unequaled Cock – Ran Kamiki
